  "time_ut": 1657363629,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d87\u0dbb\u0db9\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2 - \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Party leaders meeting begins - President is told to resign",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In order to discuss the future measures to be taken as a country under the current crisis situation, the party leaders of the Parliament started the meeting under the chairmanship of Mr. Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena.",
        "The party leaders have basically decided to request President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to resign from his position."
      ],
